🏡 Home Decor Products - MERN Stack Project
A full-featured E-commerce web application built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js), showcasing stylish and elegant home decor products such as furniture, lighting, wall art, and more.

📦 Features
🛍️ Browse Products: Explore a variety of home decor items with images, prices, and detailed descriptions.

🔍 Search & Filter: Find products by name, category, or price range.

🛒 Cart System: Add, update, and remove products from the cart.

💳 Secure Checkout: Integrated PayPal/Stripe payment system.

👤 User Authentication: Login, registration, JWT-based auth.

🧑‍💻 Admin Panel:

Manage Products (Create, Edit, Delete)

View & Update Orders

Manage Users

🌐 Responsive Design: Mobile-first, fully responsive layout.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend:

React.js

Redux Toolkit

React Router

Bootstrap / Tailwind CSS

Backend:

Node.js

Express.js

MongoDB with Mongoose

Other Tools:

JSON Web Token (JWT) for authentication

Multer / Cloudinary for image uploads

dotenv for environment configuration
